These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, reading, skydiving, writing
There 4 different types of food: tomato, watermelon, cherry, potato
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, august, march, june
1. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
5. the person eating cherry is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person eating potato and the person who's hobby is hiking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Hobby         | writing      | hiking | reading | skydiving |
| Food   | cherry | tomato  | watermelon   | potato    |
| Birthday     | february     | march    | june    | august      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, singing, sudoku, video-games
4 different games are played: canasta, billiard, chess, whist
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, badminton, climbing, skiing
1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person playing chess##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
7. the person playing canasta is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is singing##2
8. the person playing whist is between the person playing billiard and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | video-games | sudoku   | singing | dancing  |
| Game   | chess     | canasta | whist  | billiard |
| Sport     | skiing        | climbing  | badminton    | soccer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
4 different games are played: chess, bridge, snooker, go
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, white, red, purple
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, roller, snowmobile, train
1. the person who likes purple is between the person playing chess and the person playing go##2
2. the person who likes white is the person driving the train##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is the person playing snooker##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person playing go##1
5. the person playing go is in an odd position##4
6. the person who likes red is between the person playing bridge and the person who likes aquamarine##2
7. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Game          | chess | bridge   | go     | snooker     |
| Color   | white  | purple | red   | aquamarine  |
| Transport     | train      | roller | snowmobile | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, aconite, daisy, rose
4 different games are played: domino, poker, scrabble, chess
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, rowing, tennis, water-polo
1. the person playing chess is in an even position##4
2. the person who growsaconite is the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person who growsdaisy##3
5. the person playing chess is the person who's sport is badminton##1
6. the person who growsdaisy is the person playing domino##1
7. the person playing scrabble is the person who growssunflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Flower   | sunflower  | rose   | daisy     | aconite |
| Game   | scrabble  | chess      | domino        | poker     |
| Sport         | tennis | badminton | water-polo | rowing   |

