.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
House: wooden, futuristic, cottage, townhouse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, rugby, swimming, volleyball
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, tiparillo, bolivar, bongani
1. the townhouse house is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the cottage house is in an odd position##4
3. the alhambra-smoker is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the alhambra-smoker is in an even position##4
6. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left##1
7. the futuristic house is on the far right##1
8. the cottage house is on the left or right of the bolivar-smoker##3
9. the person who's sport is golf is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| House   | wooden   | townhouse   | cottage | futuristic |
| Sport         | rugby      | volleyball | golf      | swimming |
| Cigar     | tiparillo | alhambra        | bongani       | bolivar  |

