.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, sports, romance, animation
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, march, october, december
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, guinea-pig, hamster, rat
1. the person watching sports movies is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is the person watching sports movies##1
4. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far right##1
6. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
7. the person watching animation movies is in an even position##4
8. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre    | romance   | animation      | sports       | zombie |
| Birthday   | november | december | october     | march |
| Pet     | rat     | guinea-pig  | chinchilla | hamster |

