.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, lemonade, tea
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, scientist, librarian, journalist
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, tram, motorbike, train
1. the person driving the motorbike is the mechanic##1
2. the person driving the tram is between the journalist and the person driving the bike##2
3. the journalist is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the scientist is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
5. the person drinking 7up is in an even position##4
6. the journalist is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
7. the mechanic is the person drinking 7up##1
8. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | lemonade   | tea          | hot-chocolate | 7up        |
| Job   | librarian     | scientist | journalist   | mechanic     |
| Transport           | bike | tram         | train         | motorbike |

