.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
4 different games are played: bridge, mah-jongg, whist, snooker
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, librarian, scientist, social-worker
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, balloon-flower, sunflower, daffodil
1. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3
2. the scientist is the person playing bridge##1
3. the social-worker is the person playing whist##1
4. the person playing whist is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
5. the person who growsballoon-flower is between the journalist and the person playing bridge##2
6. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left or right of the scientist##3
7. the person playing bridge is in an even position##4
8. the person playing bridge is between the person playing mah-jongg and the person playing whist##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Game         | mah-jongg | bridge      | whist       | snooker    |
| Job           | librarian  | scientist  | social-worker | journalist |
| Flower   | daffodil      | sunflower | balloon-flower         | iris    |

