.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, iced-tea, water
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, thriller, spy, satire
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, july, may, february
1. the person watching adventure movies is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3
3. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
7. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
8. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
9. the person watching satire movies is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Beverage   | fanta         | coffee  | iced-tea     | water         |
| Movie-Genre        | satire | thriller | adventure | spy         |
| Birthday      | july         | may  | april   | february |

