.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, electronic, indie, punk
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, software-developer, engineer, architect
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, chess, billiard, go
 1. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
 2. the project-manager is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person playing chess is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 4. the engineer is between the fan of electronic and the fan of country##2
 5. the person playing go is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
 6. the person playing go is the fan of indie##1
 7. the architect is on the far right##1
 8. the fan of country is in an odd position##4
 9. the software-developer is between the fan of punk and the fan of indie##2
10. the person playing billiard is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | country  | indie    | electronic | punk    |
| Job   | project-manager | engineer | software-developer  | architect |
| Game           | billiard   | go    | mah-jongg        | chess   |

