.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
House: victorian, palace, cottage, gothic-revival
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, handball, ice-hockey, basketball
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, indonesian, italian, russian
1. the victorian house is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the russian is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
4. the person who's sport is handball is in an even position##4
5. the cottage house is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
6. the russian is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
7. the indonesian is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
8. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
9. the victorian house is on the left of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| House      | victorian                | gothic-revival  | palace | cottage   |
| Sport           | basketball | handball | baseball   | ice-hockey |
| Nationality   | indonesian         | dutch     | russian     | italian |

