.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, cherry, lime, peach
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, american, japanese, polish
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, july, october, june
1. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person eating peach##1
2. the person eating lime is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
4. the person eating lime is on the left of the american##1
5. the person who's birthday is in april is between the polish and the person who's birthday is in june##2
6. the japanese is in an even position##4
7. the person eating avocado is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | lime    | cherry  | peach  | avocado |
| Nationality   | polish | american | nigerian | japanese |
| Birthday   | october    | april     | june    | july |

