.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, electronic, reggae, ambient
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, crime, mystery, horror
4 different pets are kept: goat, horse, pony, turtle
1. the owner of the horse is between the fan of reggae and the person watching musical movies##2
2. the fan of house is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
4. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
5. the owner of the turtle is in an odd position##4
6. the fan of electronic is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
7. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
8. the person watching mystery movies is the fan of house##1
9. the person watching horror movies is between the owner of the pony and the owner of the goat##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Music-Genre      | house | reggae      | electronic  | ambient    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery   | crime | horror | musical |
| Pet           | turtle      | pony       | horse   | goat      |

