2. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking tea and the person who growsmarigold##2
3. the person who growsdahlia is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person drinking tea is in an even position##4
5. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
6. the japanese is between the person who growsmarigold and the australian##2
7. the person who growsdahlia is on the far right##1
8. the indian is in an even position##4
9. the person who growsmarigold is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage         | 7up    | mirinda | fanta  | tea  |
| Nationality   | indonesian | indian       | japanese | australian |
