.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-15::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, go, backgammon, mah-jongg
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, spanish, canadian, malaysian
4 different pets are kept: cat, guinea-pig, hamster, lizard
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person playing go##1
3. the person playing go is on the left of the spanish##1
4. the person playing backgammon is the malaysian##1
5. the person playing backgammon is on the far left##1
6. the japanese is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
7. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
8. the owner of the lizard is the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| Game      | backgammon      | go | monopoly     | mah-jongg    |
| Nationality   | malaysian | japanese      | spanish | canadian |
| Pet           | hamster   | guinea-pig  | cat     | lizard |

