.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-16::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, pumpkin, tomato, papaya
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, poppy, rose, tulip
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, car, snowmobile
1. the person eating cherry is on the left or right of the person eating pumpkin##3
2. the person who growsbegonia is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left##1
4. the person who growspoppy is on the left or right of the person eating papaya##3
5. the person eating pumpkin is between the person driving the bike and the person who growsrose##2
6. the person driving the airplane is the person who growstulip##1
7. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
8. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person eating cherry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Food    | tomato    | pumpkin     | cherry    | papaya        |
| Flower       | rose   | begonia | poppy | tulip |
| Transport   | snowmobile | car      | bike    | airplane   |

