4. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left or far right##3
5. the colombian is on the left of the german##1
6. the person driving the helicopter is in an odd position##4
7. the nigerian is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
