.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, baccarat, game, siglo
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, board-games, hiking, reading
City: new-york, rome, edinburgh, liverpool
1. the oliveros-smoker is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is reading is in an odd position##4
3. the person traveling to new-york is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
4. the game-smoker is on the far left##1
5. the baccarat-smoker is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is baking##2
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
7. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
8. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Cigar    | game    | baccarat    | oliveros  | siglo |
| Hobby   | reading | board-games | baking | hiking      |
| City     | rome   | new-york        | liverpool   | edinburgh       |

 